'''天主教克罗托内-圣瑟弗瑞娜总教区'''是[[罗马天主教|罗马天主教]]在[[意大利|意大利]]南部[[卡拉布里亚|卡拉布里亚]]大区设立的一个总教区。目前是[[天主教卡坦扎罗-斯奎拉切总教区|天主教卡坦扎罗-斯奎拉切总教区]]的附属教区。克罗托内教区成立于公元6世纪<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dcrss.html |title=''Catholic Hierarchy'' page |access-date=2008-10-28 |archive-date=2020-12-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202002445/https://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/diocese/dcrss.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

現任總主教為{{link-de|安傑洛·辣法耳·潘澤塔|Angelo Raffaele Panzetta}}，榮休總主教為{{link-it|道明·格拉齊亞尼|Domenico Graziani}}。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 07.11.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/07/191107c.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-11-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191107122841/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/11/07/191107c.html |archivedate=2019-11-07 |language=en |date=2019-11-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

